<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Brief Stratégique — Formation Continue Paramédicale</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --cream: #F5F2EC;
    --ink: #1A1915;
    --ink-secondary: #6B6860;
    --ink-tertiary: #AAA89F;
    --red: #C93C2A;
    --red-light: #F5EAE7;
    --green: #2A6B3C;
    --green-light: #E8F2EB;
    --blue: #1E4A8C;
    --blue-light: #E8EEF8;
    --amber: #9B5C0A;
    --amber-light: #FAF0E0;
    --purple: #4A2C8C;
    --purple-light: #EEEAF8;
    --border: rgba(26,25,21,0.12);
    --border-strong: rgba(26,25,21,0.22);
  }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .page {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 2rem 6rem;
  }

  .header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
  }

  .header-left {}

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
  }

  .header-meta {
    text-align: right;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .section-label::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .dot-red { background: var(--red); }
  .dot-green { background: var(--green); }
  .dot-blue { background: var(--blue); }
  .dot-amber { background: var(--amber); }

  .card-title {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .card-title.red { color: var(--red); }
  .card-title.green { color: var(--green); }
  .card-title.blue { color: var(--blue); }
  .card-title.amber { color: var(--amber); }

  .card h3 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .card p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .checklist {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .check-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .check-icon {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green-light);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .check-icon svg { width: 10px; height: 10px; }

  .star-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .star-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .star-item strong { color: var(--ink); }

  .featured-card {
    background: var(--ink);
    border: none;
    color: white;
  }

  .featured-card h3 { color: white; }
  .featured-card .card-title { color: #9FB8D8; }
  .featured-card p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }

  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .price-box {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .price-box .label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .price-box .amount {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .price-box .amount span {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .price-box .sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .fif-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .metric-box {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.875rem;
  }

  .metric-box .label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .metric-box .value {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .metric-box .sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .warning-box {
    background: var(--amber-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .warning-box p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--amber);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .auto-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .auto-box {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.875rem;
  }

  .auto-box .icon {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
  }

  .auto-box .title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }

  .auto-box .desc {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .axes-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .axe-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .axe-row.featured {
    background: var(--green-light);
  }

  .axe-row .axe-num {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    min-width: 36px;
    padding-top: 1px;
  }

  .axe-row.featured .axe-num { color: var(--green); }

  .axe-row .axe-content strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .axe-row .axe-content span {
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
  }

  .axe-row.featured .axe-content strong { color: var(--green); }

  .update-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .update-box {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.875rem;
  }

  .update-box .label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .update-box .value {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .update-box .desc {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Market section */
  .market-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .market-header {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .market-header .prof {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .market-header .count {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 24px;
  }

  .market-header .note {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
  }

  .market-header.kine { background: var(--green-light); }
  .market-header.kine .prof { color: var(--green); }
  .market-header.kine .count { color: var(--green); }

  .market-header.osteo { background: var(--purple-light); }
  .market-header.osteo .prof { color: var(--purple); }
  .market-header.osteo .count { color: var(--purple); }

  .market-header.podo { background: var(--amber-light); }
  .market-header.podo .prof { color: var(--amber); }
  .market-header.podo .count { color: var(--amber); }

  .market-header.chiro { background: #F5F2EC; }
  .market-header.chiro .prof { color: var(--ink-secondary); }
  .market-header.chiro .count { color: var(--ink-secondary); }

  .market-scenarios {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .scenario {
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .scenario.highlight {
    background: var(--blue-light);
    outline: 1.5px solid rgba(30,74,140,0.2);
  }

  .scenario .pct {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }

  .scenario.highlight .pct { color: var(--blue); }

  .scenario .clients {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .scenario .arr {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
  }

  .market-note {
    padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .total-banner {
    background: var(--ink);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .total-metric .label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .total-metric .value {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .assumptions {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .assumption-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .assumption-item:nth-last-child(-n+2) { border-bottom: none; }

  .assumption-item::before {
    content: '—';
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* Sequence */
  .sequence {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .seq-step {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .seq-step .year {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .seq-step .title {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .seq-step .desc {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media print {
    body { background: white; }
    .page { padding: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-left">
      <div class="eyebrow">Brief stratégique — v2</div>
      <h1>Recap <em>opportunité</em></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="header-meta">
      Formation continue paramédicale<br>
      France
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 1 — CE QUI CHANGE -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Ce qui est en train de disparaître</div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="dot dot-red"></div>
        <div class="card-title red">L'ANDPC ferme fin 2026</div>
      </div>
      <h3>Le financement public de la formation change de main</h3>
      <p>L'agence qui finançait les formations DPC (jusqu'à 728€/formation pour les kinés) disparaît. Un nouveau système piloté par la HAS et France Compétences prendra le relais en 2027 — mais les montants et modalités sont encore inconnus.</p>
      <p>Tendance de fond : la France s'aligne sur le reste de l'Europe, où la formation continue est un investissement individuel, pas une dépense d'État. Le budget va avoir tendance à se réduire à chaque cycle.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 2 — CE QUI NE BOUGE PAS -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Ce qui ne bougera pas</div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="checklist">
        <div class="check-item">
          <div class="check-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M2 5l2.5 2.5L8 3" stroke="#2A6B3C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div><strong style="color:#1A1915">L'obligation légale de se former</strong> — 8 actions sur 6 ans (4 axes × 2 actions), contrôlée par l'Ordre. Sanctions possibles jusqu'à la suspension d'exercice. Obligations pleinement opérationnelles depuis février 2026 seulement.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="check-item">
          <div class="check-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M2 5l2.5 2.5L8 3" stroke="#2A6B3C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div><strong style="color:#1A1915">Le refus de se déplacer</strong> — le e-learning est le format dominant chez les paras en 2026. Personne ne veut perdre une journée de cabinet pour aller en formation.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="check-item">
          <div class="check-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M2 5l2.5 2.5L8 3" stroke="#2A6B3C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div><strong style="color:#1A1915">Le FIF-PL</strong> — financé par les cotisations URSSAF des libéraux eux-mêmes (pas le budget État). Structurellement plus stable que l'ANDPC. Plafond e-learning : 450€ cœur de métier + 200€ transversal = <strong style="color:#1A1915">650€/an max</strong>.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 3 — LE MODELE -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Le modèle</div>
    <div class="card featured-card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-title" style="color:#9FB8D8">Proposition de valeur</div>
      </div>
      <h3>Accès complet à toutes les formations certifiantes de ta profession</h3>
      <p>Au lieu de courir après plusieurs plateformes et 8 attestations — un seul accès qui couvre les 4 axes obligatoires et gère toute l'admin à ta place. Tu ne t'occupes plus jamais de ta certification périodique.</p>
      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="price-box">
          <div class="label">Accès total annuel</div>
          <div class="amount">~650 €<span>/an</span></div>
          <div class="sub">Toutes formations incluses, illimité</div>
        </div>
        <div class="price-box" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12)">
          <div class="label">À l'action certifiante</div>
          <div class="amount">80–120 €<span>/action</span></div>
          <div class="sub">Sans engagement — LTV 640–960€ sur 6 ans</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 4 — FIF-PL -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Le FIF-PL — remboursement possible mais limité</div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="fif-grid">
        <div class="metric-box">
          <div class="label">Plafond e-learning</div>
          <div class="value">650 €<span style="font-size:13px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;color:var(--ink-secondary)">/an</span></div>
          <div class="sub">450€ cœur métier<br>+ 200€ transversal</div>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-box">
          <div class="label">Cagnotte annuelle estimée</div>
          <div class="value">~15 M€</div>
          <div class="sub">Toutes professions<br>paras libérales</div>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-box">
          <div class="label">Pros remboursables max</div>
          <div class="value">~17 000</div>
          <div class="sub">Sur 145 000 libéraux<br>(~12% seulement)</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="warning-box">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px"><path d="M8 6v3M8 10.5v.5M2.5 13.5h11l-5.5-11-5.5 11z" stroke="#9B5C0A" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        <p>Le pot se vide dès juillet-août. Les pros qui attendent la fin d'année paient de leur poche — même s'ils ont théoriquement droit au remboursement. C'est le pain point central que la plateforme peut résoudre.</p>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:8px">Ce que la plateforme automatise</p>
      <div class="auto-grid">
        <div class="auto-box">
          <div class="icon">⬜</div>
          <div class="title">Dossier pré-rempli</div>
          <div class="desc">Généré dès l'inscription, dans les 10 jours requis par le FIF-PL</div>
        </div>
        <div class="auto-box">
          <div class="icon">⬜</div>
          <div class="title">Alerte janvier</div>
          <div class="desc">Rappel automatique pour s'inscrire quand le pot est encore plein</div>
        </div>
        <div class="auto-box">
          <div class="icon">⬜</div>
          <div class="title">Attestation auto</div>
          <div class="desc">Envoyée dès le module terminé, remontée dans Ma Certif'Pro Santé</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 5 — CONTENU -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Le contenu — radio-anatomie comme module fondateur</div>
    <div class="card">
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-secondary);margin-bottom:0.75rem">Aucun acteur existant ne propose une formation dédiée à la lecture d'imagerie médicale spécifiquement conçue pour kinés, ostéos, chiros et podologues. C'est le module différenciateur. Pour couvrir les 4 axes obligatoires, la plateforme complète avec les autres axes.</p>
      <div class="axes-list">
        <div class="axe-row featured">
          <div class="axe-num">Axe 1</div>
          <div class="axe-content">
            <strong>Actualisation des connaissances ← module fondateur</strong>
            <span>Radio-anatomie, imagerie pathologique — différenciateur unique sur le marché</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="axe-row">
          <div class="axe-num">Axe 2</div>
          <div class="axe-content">
            <strong>Qualité des pratiques</strong>
            <span>Cas cliniques, évaluation des pratiques professionnelles (EPP)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="axe-row">
          <div class="axe-num">Axe 3</div>
          <div class="axe-content">
            <strong>Gestion des risques</strong>
            <span>Risques iatrogènes, sécurité patient, prévention</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="axe-row">
          <div class="axe-num">Axe 4</div>
          <div class="axe-content">
            <strong>Santé personnelle du soignant</strong>
            <span>Relation patient, communication, prévention burn-out</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="margin-top:0.75rem">
      <p style="font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:0.75rem">Effort de mise à jour annuel</p>
